This is the changelog for release versions of Mercury.

=====================
v1.0 / 2012-03-16
=====================

* Initial release

=====================
v1.0 / 2012-08-20
=====================

* Now works with Ice Cream Sandwich and Jelly Bean
* Added many new modules e.g. vulnerability scanners, root exploits, third party and OEM pilfer modules
* Bug fixes and optimisations
* Added features to existing functionality
* Added better in-line help and other user interface improvements
* New reflection interface with classloader. Meaning dynamic execution of Android at runtime, see the post on "Reflection Interface":<link to Mikes article>
* Command output can be saved to file
* Resource files can be loaded to automate Mercury input
* More documentation  - User guide and developer wiki
